{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore an uncharted planet with friends, discover adorable creatures, and craft your dream homes as you transform the world into a cozy paradise in this wholesome multiplayer life-sim! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Selected by GG Enterprises\u2014a company known for exploring and researching distant planets\u2014you\u2019ve been tasked with creating a vibrant community in this new world. Befriend cute and quirky creatures who gather rare resources to craft furniture, decorations, and houses, all while unlocking new technologies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Farm diverse crops, experiment with different locations, and attract even more creatures to expand your crafting abilities. When you\u2019re not busy building, challenge your friends in cute minigames like space races and laser tag! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With endless possibilities, shape your perfect slice of galactic life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/steam_header.png?t=1729777069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> <strong>Befriend and Collect Adorable Creatures!</strong> Befriend a delightful variety of cute alien creatures, each with their own personality and special abilities. Feed them, form bonds, and they\u2019ll reward your friendship by helping you gather rare resources to build and expand your home. Grow new crops and discover technologies to attract unique creatures who can unearth rare resources!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/befriend.gif?t=1729777069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" />\u00a0<strong>Collaborate With Friends or Play Solo!</strong> Play with up to 30 friends in a shared world! Collaborate on building projects, trade resources, or simply relax together as you explore and create.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> <strong>Build &amp; Decorate Your Dream Cozy Galactic Home.</strong> Have your creature friends help you gather materials to craft charming furniture and cute decorations. Play around with different layouts to design the perfect warm and welcoming spaces, both inside and out, creating a cozy home that\u2019s uniquely yours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/decorating.gif?t=1729777069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> <strong>Tend To Your Crops &amp; Grow a Budding Farm.\u00a0</strong>Tend to a variety of crops, experimenting with different ways to attract adorable new creatures. As your farm grows, you'll unlock new crafting options and create a thriving, cozy space that draws in even more companions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/farming.gif?t=1729777069\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> <strong>Customize your character.</strong> From your clothes to your hairstyle, you'll be able to create a unique look that's all your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/outfits.gif?t=1729777069\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> <strong>Play Fun Minigames!\u00a0</strong>Take a break from building and farming to engage in playful minigames like space races, laser tag, and more! Compete or cooperate with friends for a lighthearted, fun experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/extras/star_bullet.png?t=1729777069\" /> And much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729777069","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/page.bg.jpg?t=1729777069","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/a0b842c1b77dd6fc545ae33b8ce61c876cac4c4a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729777069","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012390/a0b842c1b77dd6fc545ae33b8ce61c876cac4c4a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729777069","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore an uncharted planet with friends, discover adorable creatures, and craft your dream homes as you transform the world into a cozy paradise in this wholesom